atilde; Thủ Dầu Một) v&agrave; c&aacute;c thiếu nhi phật tử trong ban văn h&oacute;a ch&ugrave;a Quan &Acirc;m (huyện T&acirc;n Uy&ecirc;n) với những ca kh&uacute;c trữ t&igrave;nh, ngọt ng&agrave;o ca ngợi c&ocirc;ng ơn trời biển của cha mẹ, khiến cho tất cả những ai c&oacute; mặt đều nghẹn ng&agrave;o x&uacute;c động.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 10pt; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; line-height: 18pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 10pt; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; line-height: 18pt; text-align: center; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;"><span class="content" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; font-family: verdana, arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 18pt; overflow: hidden; text-align: justify; width: 620px; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;"><img alt="" border="0" src="http://chuaphuclam.vn/images/stories/2012/T9/vulan%2015.jpg" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;" /></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 10pt; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; line-height: 18pt; text-align: center; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;"><span class="content" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; font-family: verdana, arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); 